en.title: When I left my job in advance  I woke up Bogo.
en.description:
Welcome to the â€Wang Zi Xiao suâ€ channel this is your paradise to get rid of the routine of the office!
With humor and joy as the theme our channel focuses on everyday and funny moments in the workplace bringing you a relaxed and pleasant working atmosphere.

Our unique selling point lies in the things you can do in your spare time in the office-from fishing skills at work to wits with your boss and all kinds of small games played in the office. Here's a guide to survival for full-time employees as well as day-to-day fun with teasing colleagues.

We promise to update every day to make sure you have fresh jokes and workplace tips every day. Our content is not only for laughter but also to find relaxation and self in the tense work.
If you are interested in our relaxed and intelligent office life please subscribe to the â€Wang Zi Xiao suâ€ channel!

SUBSCRIBE & ADOPT A KATANA WITH THE LINK IN BIO!!

Thank you  @beltways_inc !  Follow: â–¶ï¸ Instagram: @beltways_inc 
â–¶ï¸Website: www.beltways.com

If you love katana unboxing, then you'll love this. See the Katanas slice in action as satisfying as ASMR! These aren't rusted katanas! Sword-making, blacksmithing, knife making, and katana making are Mini Katana's passions! Be like your favorite hero in Wild Heart, Blox fruit, or Elden ring, and test your slicing skill with a Karakuri Katana, Nodachi, cursed dual katana, moonveil katana build, rivers of blood katana, or the true triple katana. Forget how to make paper katanas or lego katanas these are real carbon steel! Subscribe to watch mini katana unboxing, how to make a katana with cardboard and with paper, and more!  The Mini Katana Store is committed to high quality carbon steel blades and giving you slice of life looks as we try not to laugh challenge. Trust, Mini Katana knows how to make kunai and how to make a sword!
